  "description": "<p>Thank you for taking this exam, which is designed to help assess the formation that we are trying to impart to you through the core curriculum.&nbsp; Each of the courses in the core has a different assessment exam that is administered both at the beginning and the end of the semester.&nbsp; Your grade on this exam will have no bearing on your grade in the course in which you took the exam.&nbsp; Your teacher may assign some value to simply taking the exam (or not), but how well you do on the exam does not matter to your grade in the course.&nbsp; We will use the data from the exam to help us analyze and improve the way in which we deliver the formation, that the Theology core is designed to impart.</p><script src=\"https://instructure-uploads-pdx.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/account_167370000000000001/attachments/204385/google_analytics.js\"></script>",
